1 Section 1. There is hereby appropriated $500,000 from the General
2 Fund for FY2026-27 to the Military Department, for Program 544, to aid in
3 carrying out the provisions of the Nebraska Nonprofit Security Grant
4 Program.
5 There is included in the appropriation to this program for FY2026-27
6 $450,000 General Funds for state aid, which shall only be used for such
7 purpose.
8 Total expenditures for permanent and temporary salaries and per
9 diems from funds appropriated in this section shall not exceed $45,000
10 for FY2026-27.
